cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use or reference this framework, please cite it as below."
title: "Higgins Unity Framework (HUF)"
abstract: >-
  A mathematical framework for ratio-state monitoring under the unity
  constraint (Σρᵢ = 1). Provides MC-4 drift detection, sufficiency
  conditions, six failure modes, and deployment across domains including
  wetland ecology, transit, storage, and machine learning.
type: software
authors:
